org.osate.aadl2

Interface ProcessType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Classifier, ComponentClassifier, ComponentType, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FeatureClassifier, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, Namespace, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Process, ProcessClassifier, ProcessSubcomponentType, SubcomponentType, Type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProcessTypeImpl

    public interface ProcessType
extends ComponentType, ProcessClassifier
    A representation of the model object 'Process Type'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Data Port
    • Owned Event Data Port
    • Owned Event Port
    • Owned Data Access
    • Owned Subprogram Access
    • Owned Subprogram Group Access

    See Also:
    Aadl2Package.getProcessType()
